4) For each cmdb_id compute these aggregates: total_anomaly_points (sum of anomaly points across all its KPIs in-window), distinct_kpi_count_with_anomalies, earliest_anomaly_timestamp (minimum anomaly timestamp for that cmdb_id), max_value_overall_in_window, min_value_overall_in_window.
